fields.name: Naive Bayes
fields.description: Naive Bayes classifier. Naive Bayes is a simple probabilistic classifier based on applying the Bayes' theorem.

fields.name: REP Tree
fields.description: Widget implementing a REP Tree, which is a fast decision tree learner. Builds a decision/regression tree using information gain/variance and prunes it using reduced-error pruning (with backfitting). Only sorts values for numeric attributes once. Missing values are dealt with by splitting the corresponding instances into pieces (i.e. as in C4.5).

fields.name: Random Tree
fields.description: A tree that considers K randomly chosen attributes at each node, and performs no pruning.

fields.name: RandomForest
fields.description: Random Forest learner.

fields.name: SMO
fields.description: A support vector classifier, trained using a sequential minimal optimization algorithm.
